narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: reading of one or two plays a week and discussion in a small meeting with professor biggs, then a presentation of scenes at the end of the semester. satisfying to read the plays and then be able to act some of them (i took the acting track)
